# stemmatology : an R stemmatology package
# Version: 0.2.2 (pre-alpha)
# Date: 2014-07-16
# Author: Jean-Baptiste Camps ; Florian Cafiero
# Maintainer: complain to <jbcamps@hotmail.com>, <florian.cafiero@polytechnique.edu>
# Description: This package helps building and analysing the genealogy of textual traditions.
# License: CC BY-NC-SA 3.0

# This repository contains the source file of the development version for the project of a stemmatology package for R. This package will contain functions for the PCC method as described in Jean-Baptiste Camps And Florian Cafiero, « Genealogical Variant Locations And Simplified Stemma: A Test Case », 2014. It aims to implement as well other stemmatological method (see roadmap at http://graal.hypotheses.org/XXXX).

